      <title>服务器部署hexo流程</title>
      <link href="/2025/01/06/%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hexo%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B/"/>
      <url>/2025/01/06/%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hexo%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="阿里云服务器部署hexo"><a href="#阿里云服务器部署hexo" class="headerlink" title="阿里云服务器部署hexo"></a>阿里云服务器部署hexo</h1><p>安装需要的依赖：<br>yum install -y curl-devel expat-devel gettext-devel openssl-devel zlib-devel<br>安装编译工具：<br>yum install -y gcc perl-ExtUtils-MakeMaker package<br>检查Git是否安装：<br>git –version<br>安装Git：已经安装过的可以跳过这一步<br>yum install git -y<br>添加用户并设置密码：<br>useradd git<br>passwd git<br>创建博客目录：<br>mkdir &#x2F;home&#x2F;blog<br>给博客目录增加相应读写权限：<br>chmod -R a+rw &#x2F;home&#x2F;blog<br>建立Git仓库：<br>cd &#x2F;home&#x2F;git<br>git init –bare blog.git<br>给Git目录增加相应读写权限：<br>chmod -R a+rw &#x2F;home&#x2F;git<br>新建钩子文件：<br>vim &#x2F;home&#x2F;git&#x2F;blog.git&#x2F;hooks&#x2F;post-receive<br>在文件中添加：<br>git –work-tree&#x3D;&#x2F;home&#x2F;blog –git-dir&#x3D;&#x2F;home&#x2F;git&#x2F;blog.git checkout -f<br>给钩子文件增加可执行权限：<br>chmod +x &#x2F;home&#x2F;git&#x2F;blog.git&#x2F;hooks&#x2F;post-receive<br>安装Nginx：<br>yum install nginx -y<br>启动Nginx：<br>systemctl start nginx.service<br>查看Nginx配置文件路径：<br>nginx -t<br>修改Nginx的配置文件：<br>vim &#x2F;etc&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;nginx.conf (自己主机上的Nginx的配置文件路径)<br>重启Nginx：<br>systemctl restart nginx.service<br>在Windows端博客目录下安装部署插件：<br>npm install hexo-deployer-git –save<br>修改Hexo的配置文件：<br>deploy:<br>type: git<br>repository: git用户名@服务器IP地址:&#x2F;home&#x2F;git&#x2F;blog.git</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
